data.description: Come on out to 6333 FM 521, country living at its finest. Nestled on 6 fully fenced acres just on the outskirts of Brazoria, Tx. This custom built home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a mud/laundry room. The kitchen offers granite counter tops and all electric appliances. Outside you will find a sitting patio overlooking a stocked pond, a 40x60 steel shop with an office/guest room, 25x40 attached canopy with a concrete slab for your RV/storage. Property has an electric entry gate, NEW lighted cattle pens, 12x24 hay barn with a 24x24 canopy where the 700’ well is located and a back-up generator that will run the entire house. The opportunity to make this one yours, wont last long! Call to see it today!
